[petrenko]
; Duty - General Petrenko buy multipliers.
; Russian ecosystem is doctrine — he pays well for anything his soldiers can use.
; NATO is a liability: wrong ammo, wrong supply chain, ideologically suspect.
; Zone items are not bought. Duty does not traffic in anomaly products. Ever.
; Military discipline means repair, medical, and ammo are always in demand.
; Normalized to 1.0 max. General trader_discount applied separately.

